{"title":"JDBC链接数据库的5个步骤","slug":"JDBC链接数据库的5个步骤","date":"2019-11-10T15:58:25.000Z","updated":"2019-11-24T03:42:08.123Z","comments":true,"excerpt":"","content":"<h2 id=\"jsp连接数据库的步骤\"><a href=\"#jsp连接数据库的步骤\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"jsp连接数据库的步骤\"></a>jsp连接数据库的步骤</h2><h3 id=\"1-首先创建一个新的jsp文件和数据表\"><a href=\"#1-首先创建一个新的jsp文件和数据表\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.首先创建一个新的jsp文件和数据表\"></a>1.首先创建一个新的jsp文件和数据表</h3><p>注意：这些步骤都是在部署好服务器的前提下做的，一般我们使用的都是Tomcat服务器</p>\n<h3 id=\"2-加载数据库驱动\"><a href=\"#2-加载数据库驱动\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.加载数据库驱动\"></a>2.加载数据库驱动</h3><figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">Class.forName(<span class=\"string\">\"org.gjt.mm.mysql.Driver\"</span>);  </span><br><span class=\"line\"> out.print(<span class=\"string\">\"成功加载驱动\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\"> String url=<span class=\"string\">\"jdbc:mysql://127.0.0.1:3306/test?user=root&amp;password=123567&amp;useSSL=false\"</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//myaql是数据库名</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//3306是端口号</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//user后面是用户名</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//password是密码</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"3-获取数据库连接\"><a href=\"#3-获取数据库连接\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3.获取数据库连接\"></a>3.获取数据库连接</h3><figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"> Connection conn=DriverManager.getConnection(url);</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//让java可以操作数据库</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"4-定义一个sql命令\"><a href=\"#4-定义一个sql命令\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"4.定义一个sql命令\"></a>4.定义一个sql命令</h3><figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">Statement stmt = <span class=\"keyword\">null</span>;  </span><br><span class=\"line\"> ResultSet rs = <span class=\"keyword\">null</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"5-查询语句\"><a href=\"#5-查询语句\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"5.查询语句\"></a>5.查询语句</h3><figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">String sql = <span class=\"string\">\"SELECT * FROM student;\"</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"> <span class=\"comment\">//student是你创建的表的名称   </span></span><br><span class=\"line\"> stmt = conn.createStatement();  </span><br><span class=\"line\"> rs = stmt.executeQuery(sql);  </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">while</span>(rs.next())</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t out.print(<span class=\"string\">\"&lt;br&gt;\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tout.println(rs.getInt(<span class=\"number\">1</span>));</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tout.println(rs.getString(<span class=\"number\">2</span>));</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"6-关闭数据库连接\"><a href=\"#6-关闭数据库连接\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"6.关闭数据库连接\"></a>6.关闭数据库连接</h3><figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">stmt.close();</span><br><span class=\"line\"> rs.close();</span><br><span class=\"line\"> conn.close();</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//关闭数据库，便于以后操作</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>就这样就可以连接到数据库了</p>\n","categories":[],"tags":[]}